  "1785270": {
    "name": "L.O.L. Surprise! B.B. 为旅行而生™ ",
    "steam_appid": 1785270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/d5c7171891004ff2b6c3f64335659f1c.webp?t=1727089158\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>全世界的粉丝都等不及要拆箱自己的 L.O.L. Surprise! 娃娃了，而你可以让他们梦想成真！选择角色，收集劲爆的娃娃和亮片、爱心、钻石等饰物，让 L.O.L. Surprise! 娃娃商店化为现实。无论你多大年龄，劲爆 L.O.L. Surprise! 娃娃制造者那里都能给你带来足够的挑战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/7cf0effa834600d015f18bbf98699f18.poster.avif?t=1727089158\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/7cf0effa834600d015f18bbf98699f18.webm?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/7cf0effa834600d015f18bbf98699f18.mp4?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/67a0d1b4805ce2bdd5e6696bf603677c.webp?t=1727089158\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>这场世界之旅充满惊喜！完成每个关卡时都将获得新角色和贴纸奖励，然后在绝妙的时装秀和演唱会上加以展示。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/f818d89168ba526361cb283278a2737c.poster.avif?t=1727089158\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/f818d89168ba526361cb283278a2737c.webm?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/f818d89168ba526361cb283278a2737c.mp4?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/a664d4ed6fa290c440525d59279e930d.webp?t=1727089158\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>你甚至可以在这场世界之旅中与好友组队，支持最多四名玩家同屏合作进行游戏。你可以畅玩五座城市中的 30 个关卡，迅速建立自己的 L.O.L. Surprise! 收藏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/ae7a12c8b7bd292390ca01957251dc6b.poster.avif?t=1727089158\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/ae7a12c8b7bd292390ca01957251dc6b.webm?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/ae7a12c8b7bd292390ca01957251dc6b.mp4?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>扮演你最喜爱的角色 – 化身 L.O.L. Surprise! 娃娃，解锁角色的特别版<br></li><li>接受挑战 – 你能否将粉丝们梦寐以求的 L.O.L. Surprise! 球送到他们手上？<br></li><li>环游世界 – 跨越五座新的城市，畅玩30个关卡，包括新众创城、皇后岛和霓虹沙漠等等。<br></li><li>表演节目 – 在时装秀和演唱会上展示你的收藏<br></li><li>与好友欢聚 – 最多 4 名玩家可在 L.O.L. Surprise! 娃娃商店中组队！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/31ea42bbe174433518c07e5010fbcc7b.poster.avif?t=1727089158\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/31ea42bbe174433518c07e5010fbcc7b.webm?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785270/extras/31ea42bbe174433518c07e5010fbcc7b.mp4?t=1727089158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
